<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-5951] Camel-syslog dataformat broken with netty transport</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-5951</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;in Rfc3164SyslogDataFormat, the remoteAddress of the SyslogMessage is set from the Mina or Netty headers. There&apos;s a copy/paste error for Netty: it correctly checks for the existence of the CamelNettyRemoteAddress header, but then attempts to set the remoteAddress from a CamelMinaRemoteAddress header.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(there&apos;s no camel-syslog component in JIRA)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
